ActIndian Act
SubjectNenagwas Indian Reserve No. 12, British Columbia ** Creation **
PrecisOrder setting apart 256.8 hectares (634.6 acres) of lands, for the use and benefit of the Tlowitsis Tribe as creation of NENAGWAS INDIAN RESERVE NO. 12, located in the Strathcona Regional District and is adjacent to the City of Campbell River, British Columbia.
